<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WeDo File Upload API</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .description {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #2575fc;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn i {
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        
        .tech-list {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .tech-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
        
        @@keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
        
        @@media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .subtitle { font-size: 1.2rem; }
            .description { font-size: 1rem; }
            .btn { padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
            .tech-list { gap: 15px; }
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <i class="fas fa-cloud-upload-alt"></i>
        </div>
        
        <h1>WeDo File Upload API</h1>
        
        <p class="subtitle">
            API RESTful para upload e gerenciamento de arquivos
        </p>
        
        <p class="description">
            Uma solução completa e segura para armazenamento de arquivos em servidor. 
            Desenvolvida com ASP.NET Core, oferece endpoints robustos para upload, 
            download e gerenciamento de arquivos com validações e segurança.
        </p>
        
        <a href="/Doc" class="btn">
            Ver Documentação da API
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
        
        <div class="tech-list">
            <div class="tech-item">ASP.NET Core</div>
            <div class="tech-item">Entity Framework</div>
            <div class="tech-item">SQL Server</div>
            <div class="tech-item">REST API</div>
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            <p>© 2026 WeDo File Upload API | Versão 1.0.0</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>